Properties.Caption: Просмотр заявок на кассовый расход
Properties.Tag: Select [DOC].[CDOC] As [Документ], [DOC].[DDOC] As [Дата документа], [UFK_ZR].[KBK_PAY] As [БК плательщика], [UFK_ZR].[KBK_RCP] As [БК получателя], [K_TS].[CUL] As [Получатель], Max([K_TS].[NUL]) As [Наименование получателя], Sum([UFK_ZR].[SUM_DOC]) As [Сумма заявки], [UFK_ZR].[UnloadDate] As [Дата/время выгрузки], [UFK_ZR].[SaveDate] As [Дата/время сохранения] From (((((([UFK_ZR] With (NoLock) Inner Join [K_UL_K_UL] With (NoLock) On ([UFK_ZR].[K_UL_K_ULID]=[K_UL_K_UL].[K_UL_K_ULID])) Inner Join [K_TS] With (NoLock) On ([UFK_ZR].[K_TSID]=[K_TS].[K_TSID])) Inner Join [K_BN] With (NoLock) On ([K_TS].[K_BNID]=[K_BN].[K_BNID])) Inner Join [DOC] With (NoLock) On ([UFK_ZR].[DOCID]=[DOC].[DOCID])) Inner Join [Apps_Groups] With (NoLock) On ([DOC].[Apps_GroupsID]=[Apps_Groups].[Apps_GroupsID])) Inner Join [K_TD] With (NoLock) On ([DOC].[K_TDID]=[K_TD].[K_TDID])) Where [K_UL_K_UL].[CUL_PARENT] Like GetCUL() And [K_TD].[CTD]='KA' And |0 Group by [DOC].[CDOC], [DOC].[DDOC], [UFK_ZR].[KBK_PAY], [UFK_ZR].[KBK_RCP], [K_TS].[CUL], [UFK_ZR].[UnloadDate], [UFK_ZR].[SaveDate] Order by |1
Properties.Name: Просмотр заявок на кассовый расход
